data.title: This Is What a Pro Lacrosse Player Eats for Breakfast
data.meta_description: Kevin Buchanan, a Boston Cannons lacrosse player, eats this meal to fuel up for game day. Kevin Buchanan is a midfielder with the Cannons.
data.text:
This meal gets Kevin Buchanan ready for game day.

We don’t need to tell you that breakfast is the most important meal of the day. In this series, we’re asking some of Boston’s top doctors, fitness pros, and dietitians for a sneak peek into their kitchens, so we can see what’s on their breakfast table.

Kevin Buchanan

Claim to Fame: He’s a midfielder for the Boston Cannons, Boston’s professional lacrosse team. Before that, he played for Ohio State University.

What He Ate: Oatmeal pancakes with a berry and Greek yogurt smoothie.
